    "en": {
      "title": "Russian sanctions are not a successful answer to the conflict",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Hungarian Prime Minister Viktor Orb\u00e1n says the European Union needs a new strategy for the conflict in Ukraine as sanctions against Russia have not worked.",
        "\"A new strategy is needed to draft a good peace proposal, focusing on peace talks instead of winning the war,\" Orban said in a speech in Romania."
      ],
